<%- include('partials/header', { pageTitle: 'Our Family Story' }) %>
<section class="section">
  <div class="container narrow">
    <header class="section-header">
      <p class="section-eyebrow">Capoccia · Miotto</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">Our Family Story</h2>
      <div class="section-rule"></div>
    </header>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem">The Capoccia and Miotto families share Italian heritage. Their reunion tradition began in <strong>1977</strong> and continues as a gift to every generation.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1rem">The Capoccia and Miotto branches were joined when <strong>Anna M. Capoccia</strong> married <strong>Amerigo “Mickey” Miotto</strong>, creating the family bond this website proudly honors. Anna’s brothers, <strong>George Capoccia</strong> and <strong>Tony Capoccia</strong>, remain central to that living connection.</p>
    <p style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">Both families are honored equally on this tribute. As names, photographs, and stories are contributed and reviewed, this page will grow into a fuller account of our shared history.</p>

    <div class="form-card" style="margin-bottom:1.5rem">
      <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:1.45rem;color:var(--burgundy);margin-bottom:0.75rem">Family Tree Snippet</h3>
      <p style="margin-bottom:0.5rem;color:var(--ink-soft)"><strong>Capoccia Parents → Costanzo &amp; Madeline</strong></p>
      <ul style="list-style:none;padding-left:0;color:var(--ink-soft);line-height:1.8">
        <li>├── <a href="/family-members" style="color:var(--burgundy);font-weight:600">Tony</a> (m. Fran Babich) – honored elder</li>
        <li>├── <strong>George</strong> (m. Christine) – Capoccia Patriarch &amp; Matriarch</li>
        <li>└── <strong>Anna</strong> (m. Mickey Miotto) – Miotto Matriarch (link to Miotto branch)</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="hint" style="margin-top:0.75rem">A fuller interactive family tree will grow as verified relationship details are shared. We will not invent connections.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="empty">
      <h3>Help us complete the next chapters.</h3>
      <p>Family members are invited to contribute names, photographs, dates, stories, documents, recipes, traditions, and memories that will help us preserve the history of the Capoccia and Miotto families.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="/contribute/story">Help Tell Our Family Story</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
